{"tid":2133290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太平花園女確診者零晨回家後今早9點多由救護車送院","createTime":"2020-07-31T03:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T06:02:43.000Z","uid":22556,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4373dd4a550a9a196edaa374c0bd73fde80706fa","tid":2133290,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T03:51:00.000Z","msg":"事發於周四（30日）晚上11時許，警方接獲太平道2號太平花園業主立案法團報案，指1名確診女住客離開大廈。警方身穿保護衣及護目鏡登樓調查，未有尋獲涉案女患者，其後收隊離去，並將案件列作「雜項」處理。現場消息指該名女子凌晨2時許自行回家。<br />\n<br />\n及至早上8時45分，消防派出救護車到太平花園處理一宗傳染病個案，9時40分左右將1名女子帶走，送往東區醫院。女子頭戴鴨舌帽，全身由藍色墊包裹，低頭自行步上救護車。清潔工緊隨其後，在大廈一帶洗街消毒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/505072/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E8%8A%B1%E5%9C%92%E5%A5%B3%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E8%80%85%E6%93%85%E9%9B%A2%E4%BD%8F%E6%89%80-%E7%94%B1%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7%E8%BB%8A%E6%8E%A5%E8%B5%B0-%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E5%B7%A5%E6%B4%97%E8%A1%97?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F505072%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%259C%2592%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%2593%2585%25E9%259B%25A2%25E4%25BD%258F%25E6%2589%2580-%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%2595%2591%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%258E%25A5%25E8%25B5%25B0-%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25BD%2594%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%25B4%2597%25E8%25A1%2597%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dnews&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG134WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=bc60cce2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/505072/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E8%8A%B1%E5%9C%92%E5%A5%B3%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E8%80%85%E6%93%85%E9%9B%A2%E4%BD%8F%E6%89%80-%E7%94%B1%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7%E8%BB%8A%E6%8E%A5%E8%B5%B0-%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E5%B7%A5%E6%B4%97%E8%A1%97?utm_medium=Social&amp;